{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"017dcf2dd6","title":"我反对共产党一党专政","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e0483e2d91","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"017dcf2dd6"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"0cf3a02c6c","name":"王明欣"},{"id":"b9d6e9c96b","name":"北京政法学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b2f9dc17ed","type":"title","text":"我反对共产党一党专政","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"017dcf2dd6"},{"id":"22e14e22ba","type":"authors","text":"北京政法学院王明欣","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"017dcf2dd6"},{"id":"307472b2cd","type":"subtitle","text":"（摘录，标题为编者所加）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"017dcf2dd6"},{"id":"483111992d","type":"paragraph","text":"我反对共产党一党专政、党员独裁。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"017dcf2dd6"},{"id":"68c69301a9","type":"paragraph","text":"长期共存，互相监督，不过是形式而已，民主党派有职无权，实际上是一党专政。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"017dcf2dd6"},{"id":"277ad2de94","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政我不否认，但我反对共产党领导的无产阶级专政，无产阶级专政不一定要共产党领导。我们的国家是全国人民的国家，不是共产党的国家。呼吁改变民主党派的地位。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"017dcf2dd6"},{"id":"4755214aa9","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政一方面是无产阶级的领导，另一方面群众积极参加。这就是说，群众也可以领导，可是实际上属于领导地位的都是党员……。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"017dcf2dd6"},{"id":"1d27307458","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等党校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"017dcf2dd6"}],"page":{"id":"669fcf0de0","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"017dcf2dd6","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}